<div class="page-content post-wrap">
  <a href="../blog.html" class="back-link">← Back to Blog</a>

  <!-- CHANGE THIS: hero image -->
  <img class="post-hero" src="../photos/YOURPHOTO-hero.jpg" alt="Description"/>

  <!-- CHANGE THIS: date, location, camera -->
  <div class="post-meta">Month Year &nbsp;·&nbsp; City, Country &nbsp;·&nbsp; Camera Name</div>

  <!-- CHANGE THIS: post title -->
  <h1 class="post-title">Your Post Title Here</h1>

  <div class="post-body">

    <!-- CHANGE THIS: your writing -->
    <p>Your opening paragraph. Set the scene — where are you, what time is it, what were you looking for?</p>

    <!-- Full-width photo with caption -->
    <figure class="photo">
      <img src="../photos/YOURPHOTO-1.jpg" alt="Description"/>
      <figcaption>Location or context · Camera · Film</figcaption>
    </figure>

    <p>Second paragraph. What happened next? What did you notice that surprised you?</p>

    <!-- Two photos side by side -->
    <figure class="photo duo">
      <img src="../photos/YOURPHOTO-2.jpg" alt="Description"/>
      <img src="../photos/YOURPHOTO-3.jpg" alt="Description"/>
      <figcaption>Optional caption for both</figcaption>
    </figure>

    <p>Third paragraph. Go deeper — what does this place or moment mean to you?</p>

    <!-- Pull quote — a line that stands out -->
    <div class="pull-quote">Write a line here that captures the feeling of the shoot.</div>

    <p>Another paragraph. More photos, more story.</p>

    <!-- Three photos in a row -->
    <figure class="photo trio">
      <img src="../photos/YOURPHOTO-4.jpg" alt=""/>
      <img src="../photos/YOURPHOTO-5.jpg" alt=""/>
      <img src="../photos/YOURPHOTO-6.jpg" alt=""/>
    </figure>

    <p>Closing paragraph. Reflection — what would you do differently, what will you remember?</p>

    <!-- Final full-width closer -->
    <figure class="photo">
      <img src="../photos/YOURPHOTO-final.jpg" alt="Description"/>
      <figcaption>Final caption</figcaption>
    </figure>

  </div>

  <!-- CHANGE THIS: link to previous and next posts -->
  <nav class="post-nav">
    <a href="previous-post.html">← Previous post</a>
    <a href="next-post.html">Next post →</a>
  </nav>
</div>

